      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under version control with documented verification test suite passing at release. MRL 2 requires Gradation 2: documented QA plan with regression testing.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional software QA plan. Version control via Git; 47-case regression suite executed and passed at release. SQA documentation reviewed and archived in project record."
    },
    {
