      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, Gradation 1 is acceptable. Equivalency between validation and COU inputs need only be acknowledged.",
      "rationale": "Blood analog (glycerin-water) used in validation versus whole blood in COU. Viscosity matched at 37 °C. Red blood cell deformability effects not captured in analog; acknowledged as known physics gap. Gradation 1 accepted at MRL 2; model-form uncertainty estimate absorbs this gap."
    }
